about us
DLK and the Mission from Mom provides great popular music from the 50s sthru the present day delivered with love.
Know More About US
Dr Lou has been a performing artist with the Privileged Few Band for 20 years and a solo artist for 25 years. He has played thousands of shows and has a song book of more than 600 songs with over 3000 original songs. He's a veteran radio host and still maintains a show on WKDW FM 97.5 North Port FLA. Kara is a seasoned performer with stays in various bands and is an accomplished vocalist in the Florida Keys for many years.
What we do ?
We bring our love of music to people all over the world. We provide duet shows that are designed to bring quality renditions of classic songs that everyone knows and loves and they are delivered with a unique style that preserves the cadence and essence of the song and the vocals while offering a special take on the music with instrumental improvisation.
Join US
